        portrait: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0f/Kim_Il-sung_in_1950.jpg",
        note: "Started the war. Lost the war (except China saved him). Built a totalitarian state on the myth of having won the war. Created a hereditary dictatorship that has now lasted three generations. The man who started the Korean War and never suffered any personal consequence for it.",
