        note: "Declared himself **caliph** from a mosque in **Mosul** in 2014 — claiming authority over all Muslims worldwide. Built **ISIS** into a territory-holding pseudo-state with taxes, courts, and a propaganda machine that recruited **40,000** foreign fighters from 80+ countries. The caliphate was destroyed by 2019. Baghdadi was killed in a US raid in **Idlib** in October 2019 — he detonated a suicide vest rather than be captured. The caliphate lasted five years. Its influence will last longer.",
