        portrait: "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a2/Aहमद_بن_بلة.jpg",
        note: "Co-founded the FLN. Imprisoned by France for six years (his plane was intercepted — France literally hijacked a Moroccan aircraft to arrest him). Became Algeria's first president in 1962. Was overthrown by his own defense minister (**Boumediene**) in 1965. The revolutionary who liberated his country and then lost it to his own colleague. Revolutions eat their founders. It's practically a rule.",
