        note: "Invaded the Falklands to save his regime. Lost the Falklands and his regime. Removed from power in June 1982, tried and imprisoned for human rights abuses and military incompetence. Died in 2003. The general who thought a quick colonial adventure would distract from economic collapse and a dirty war. He was right about the distraction. He was wrong about everything else.",
