        note: "Founded the LTTE as a teenager. Built it into the world's most capable insurgency — with conventional military capability, a naval wing, a suicide unit, and a civil administration. Assassinated two heads of state. Rejected every peace offer. Refused to compromise. Used child soldiers. Used human shields in the final battle. **Killed** on **May 18, 2009** — shot while attempting to flee the final pocket. His body was displayed on Sri Lankan television. He was simultaneously a liberation fighter and a war criminal. The Tamil cause needed a leader. It got a dictator who chose total war over negotiated autonomy — and lost everything.",
