        note: "Former Soviet artillery officer who planned the August 1996 recapture of Grozny — the operation that ended the war. Elected Chechen president in 1997 in internationally recognized elections. Tried to moderate the independence movement and marginalize extremists like Basayev. Failed — because building a state in a destroyed country surrounded by a hostile Russia is impossible without resources, stability, or luck. He had none. Killed by Russian forces in **2005** during the second war.",
