      belligerents: "Republican paramilitaries (IRA, ~1,500) vs Loyalist paramilitaries (UVF/UDA, ~2,000) vs British security forces (~43,000 at peak) — a three-sided conflict where all sides killed civilians",
      strength: "~30,000 British Army + 13,000 RUC vs ~1,500 IRA (ratio: 30:1; stalemate lasted 25 years)",
