        note: "Rose from junior officer to dictator by eliminating every rival — reportedly shooting the Derg's first chairman at a committee meeting. Launched the **Red Terror** that killed ~500,000. Built Africa's largest army with Soviet weapons. Used **famine as a weapon** — burning crops, blockading aid, forcibly resettling populations. When the army crumbled, he fled to Zimbabwe (May 1991). Convicted of **genocide in absentia** (2006). Never extradited. Lives in a villa in Harare. The man who charged families for the bullets that killed their children has been free for 30+ years. Justice, in Ethiopia's case, is a legal finding with no practical consequence.",
