      casualties: "3–5.4 million excess deaths (deadliest conflict since WWII); ~3.4 million displaced during formal war; ~6.9 million IDPs in DRC by 2024; tens of thousands of child soldiers; systematic sexual violence; conflict minerals funding violence to this day",
