      "Teddy Roosevelt added a corollary to the Monroe Doctrine that basically said: 'Europe, stay out. Also, we're going in.' It was the geopolitical equivalent of calling dibs.",
      "The Panama Canal turned the entire Caribbean into America's front yard, and you don't let strangers rearrange your front yard.",
